OL,3,CTransport minister will not stand as
OL,4,Ccandidate in General Election
OL,6,FTransport minister Huw Merriman is the
OL,7,Flatest Conservative MP to announce he
OL,8,Fwill not seek re-election.
OL,10,FThe Bexhill and Battle MP did not
OL,11,Fspecify a reason for his departure but
OL,12,Fthanked his staff, local Conservative
OL,13,Fassociation and the Prime Minister,
OL,14,Fand paid tribute to his constituency.
OL,16,FIn a letter posted on X, he wrote: "I
OL,17,Fwish my successor well in their role
OL,18,Fas Member of Parliament.
