OL,6,F"To both the next MP for Bexhill and
OL,7,FBattle and to a future rail minister:
OL,8,Fif these roles bring even half the
OL,9,Famount of happiness as they have
OL,10,Fbrought me, then it will make you very
OL,11,Fproud."
OL,13,FIn a transport-themed sign-off, he
OL,14,Fadded: "Thank you to all of the
OL,15,Famazing people I have met on my
OL,16,Fjourney. I will miss everything but,
OL,17,Fas I sit in the political departure
OL,18,Flounge, I am looking forward to a new
OL,19,Fjourney (whatever that might be)."
