OL,6,FThe full statement on his website
OL,7,Fsaid: "After 9 years as the Member of
OL,8,FParliament for Bexhill and Battle, I
OL,9,Fhave made the decision not to stand as
OL,10,Fa candidate at the next election. This
OL,11,Fmeans I will also leave my job as Rail
OL,12,FMinister on 4 July.
OL,14,F"I have loved being an MP and I leave
OL,15,Fwith a heavy heart. The constituency
OL,16,Fis a beautiful place, with wonderful
OL,17,Fpeople in every town and village. I've
OL,18,Fbeen lucky enough to work across the
OL,19,Fcommunity, and political divide, with
OL,20,Fsome fantastic people.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/5
