OL,6,F"I've also been fortunate to have had
OL,7,Fthe best constituency staff, and
OL,8,FAssociation, an MP could ask for.
OL,10,F"Transport has been my passion
OL,11,Fthroughout my time in Parliament. I am
OL,12,Fgrateful to have served for seven
OL,13,Fyears on the Transport Select
OL,14,FCommittee, with almost three as Chair.
OL,16,F"I've loved my time as Rail Minister
OL,17,Fand am grateful to the Prime Minister
OL,18,Ffor trusting me with this important
OL,19,Fportfolio.
